Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.46,0:00:05.33,Font 1,,0,0,0,,He became a prince out of necessity.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.42,0:00:09.17,Font 1,,0,0,0,,He realized that if nothing else,\Nthe future we hoped for
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.25,0:00:15.05,Font 1,,0,0,0,,would never come unless someone became\Nthe sacrificial lamb called a "prince."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.14,0:00:19.43,Font 1,,0,0,0,,So even though it wasn't what he\Nwanted, he decided to be a prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.52,0:00:22.39,Font 1,,0,0,0,,In this world with no king...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.48,0:00:27.31,Font 1,,0,0,0,,But exactly how did he become a prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.40,0:00:31.15,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I still don't know that secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.71,0:02:09.87,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Well, here we are, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.77,0:02:29.73,Font 1,,0,0,0,,And here's your bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.33,0:02:48.29,Font 1,,0,0,0,,This is the center of the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.88,0:02:58.30,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(426,76)\fn\fs24}Episode 1 :\NI Picked Up a Prince
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.47,0:03:03.43,Font 1,,0,0,0,,It's different than I imagined, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.51,0:03:06.47,Font 1,,0,0,0,,And the fountain is way\Nfurther away than I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.47,0:03:07.68,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(269,97)\fn\fs30}Washington
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.85,0:03:11.02,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I wonder if everyone's mad at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.10,0:03:15.19,Font 1,,0,0,0,,If I had my phone on, Osugi\Nwould definitely be calling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.23,0:03:21.36,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Well, I've come this far, so I\Nhave to do what I'm here for!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.75,0:03:35.29,Font 1,,0,0,0,,No good... It's too far away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.96,0:03:42.38,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Hey! Young lady, what did you just throw?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.48,0:03:52.69,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Hey, you wanna die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.81,0:03:57.11,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Hey there, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.19,0:03:59.48,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What? For real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.57,0:04:01.94,Font 1,,0,0,0,,More like, why is he naked?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.57,0:04:08.08,Font 1,,0,0,0,,No. 9 is even more unique than I'd imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.16,0:04:09.95,Font 1,,0,0,0,,But it ends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.04,0:04:14.37,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I see. That's rather regrettable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.46,0:04:19.92,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Are you on his side? I'm jealous, Juiz.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.01,0:04:21.67,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Prepare for my return to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.76,0:04:25.30,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sir. I pray you shall continue to be a savior.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.66,0:04:51.91,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Brr, I'm cold! For that matter, I'm naked...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.00,0:04:55.12,Font 1,,0,0,0,,A cell phone and... a gun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.00,0:04:59.42,Font 1,,0,0,0,,The White House...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.50,0:05:03.76,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I remember the White House,\Nbut I don't know who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.84,0:05:07.39,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Hey! Young lady, what did you just throw?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.40,0:05:22.48,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Hey, you wanna die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.57,0:05:25.44,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Hey there, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.53,0:05:28.66,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Actually, I think I'm the one in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.12,0:05:35.75,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Was he hit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.83,0:05:37.75,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Get that guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.92,0:05:43.13,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Now's my chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.21,0:05:44.76,Font 1,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.05,0:05:51.80,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You were almost in real trouble there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.89,0:05:54.27,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You should get away while\Nyou've got the chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.81,0:05:57.85,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I-I'm not in trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.94,0:06:02.11,Font 1,,0,0,0,,But you know it's bad to throw\Nthings at the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.65,0:06:05.28,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You were watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.36,0:06:07.82,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Kind of.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.90,0:06:09.70,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.37,0:06:16.95,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Um, aren't you cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.04,0:06:18.75,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.67,0:06:25.25,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Er, I'll lend you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.27,0:06:44.57,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Are you sure? I need to get away, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.65,0:06:48.07,Font 1,,0,0,0,,It's fine. It's my thanks for helping me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.15,0:06:50.91,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Thanks. Don't mind if I do, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.04,0:06:59.66,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.18,0:07:16.68,Font 1,,0,0,0,,It's totally blank!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.77,0:07:20.39,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Isn't there some record that'll\Nhelp me figure out who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.65,0:07:27.78,Font 1,,0,0,0,,--Hello, this is Juiz.\N--Juiz? Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.86,0:07:32.40,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I'm your concierge. I thought\Nyou were just going to fade out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.49,0:07:33.82,Font 1,,0,0,0,,It sounds like you're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.91,0:07:35.62,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.70,0:07:40.25,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Hey... Do you know who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.33,0:07:42.12,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Who you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.21,0:07:44.50,Font 1,,0,0,0,,This is the first time\Nyou've erased your memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.58,0:07:47.84,Font 1,,0,0,0,,and I received no order to prepare\Na new background for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:50.84,Font 1,,0,0,0,,so I really couldn't say\Nwho you might be right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.92,0:07:52.93,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Erased my memories?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.85,0:08:02.02,Font 1,,0,0,0,,My last order was to tell you where\Nto go next, so I'm sending that to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.10,0:08:04.35,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Well then, I wish for your success
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.44,0:08:08.73,Font 1,,0,0,0,,and sincerely pray you shall\Ncontinue to be a savior.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.82,0:08:10.48,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.53,0:08:17.49,Font 1,,0,0,0,,So is this where I live, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.58,0:08:21.50,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I was so scared... what was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.58,0:08:24.75,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I guess people really\Nshouldn't do unfamiliar things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.67,0:08:30.13,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! My passport!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.21,0:08:32.34,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.42,0:08:34.59,Font 1,,0,0,0,,It's in my coat pocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.48,0:08:52.65,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Hi there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.07,0:08:56.70,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Well, considering how I'm dressed...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.78,0:09:03.50,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What do I do? I have to get it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.25,0:09:12.38,Font 1,,0,0,0,,That way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.46,0:09:14.17,Font 1,,0,0,0,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.14,0:09:22.26,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why would that guy give him his pants?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.18,0:09:26.44,Font 1,,0,0,0,,This makes no sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.49,0:09:37.03,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Woo-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.63,0:09:54.92,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.01,0:09:58.01,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Hey! Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.89,0:10:08.56,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.19,0:10:13.15,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Huh? No way, where'd he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.23,0:10:14.98,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Hey--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.20,0:10:26.70,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.79,0:10:28.41,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.50,0:10:30.79,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Dude, what do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.25,0:10:36.46,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Say, my apartment's on the second floor, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.55,0:10:39.51,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Aren't you in Room B on the third floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.22,0:10:43.22,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.31,0:10:46.39,Font 1,,0,0,0,,If I don't hurry, I'll miss my flight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.82,0:10:56.98,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What's his room number?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.07,0:10:58.32,Font 1,,0,0,0,,3B.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.40,0:11:00.03,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.16,0:11:07.54,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Hey, we got a suspicious male\Nand female couple on the loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.62,0:11:10.54,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I'm sending the pic from the security camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.05,0:11:26.68,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Aw, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.77,0:11:29.93,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I don't remember this at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.02,0:11:32.39,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Is this my apartment?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.04,0:11:50.95,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Perfect fit...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.47,0:12:10.64,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Wh-What the heck?\NWhat is this, a terrorist hideout?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.73,0:12:14.31,Font 1,,0,0,0,,It's like that movie-- what was it called again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.82,0:12:21.53,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Taxi Driver!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.61,0:12:24.61,Font 1,,0,0,0,,No, then I wouldn't be naked,\NI'd have a Mohawk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.57,0:12:28.53,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Passports?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.62,0:12:30.83,Font 1,,0,0,0,,How many are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.91,0:12:34.00,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What, instead of De Niro, I'm Jason Bourne?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.13,0:12:37.08,Font 1,,0,0,0,,They're all me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.17,0:12:40.25,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Someone's definitely setting me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.39,0:12:46.72,Font 1,,0,0,0,,For real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.80,0:12:49.22,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Am I a terrorist after all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.31,0:12:51.93,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Have I killed people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.73,0:13:04.95,Font 1,,0,0,0,,U-Um, you're the person\NI loaned my coat to, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.03,0:13:08.28,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Would you mind giving it back?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.37,0:13:12.33,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You see, my passport and\Nwallet are in the pockets.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.41,0:13:16.67,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I'll give you the coat itself,\Nso please just give those back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.75,0:13:19.54,Font 1,,0,0,0,,That's fine. Hang on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.05,0:13:31.64,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Saki Morimi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.72,0:13:34.68,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Born in 1 989, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.56,0:13:42.36,Font 1,,0,0,0,,This is the one! I'll use this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.44,0:13:46.78,Font 1,,0,0,0,,The name is... Akira Takizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.86,0:13:50.20,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Okay, from now on I'm Akira Takizawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.72,0:14:11.80,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What's he doing in there? Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.44,0:14:22.94,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Hello. I need to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.02,0:14:25.15,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.24,0:14:27.99,Font 1,,0,0,0,,The girl in this picture-- is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.74,0:14:35.37,Font 1,,0,0,0,,U-Um... Er...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:39.21,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.29,0:14:40.87,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.00,0:14:44.13,Font 1,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.21,0:14:48.63,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Wait a sec. Come this way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.89,0:14:54.56,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Are you Japanese?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.64,0:14:56.64,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I need to see your johnny.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.89,0:15:06.02,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Whoa! It sure does look like me,\Nbut where was that taken?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.90,0:15:11.91,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What do you think? I guess it is me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.20,0:15:19.91,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Have a nice date.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.00,0:15:22.12,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.92,0:15:28.34,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Okay, have a good one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.42,0:15:31.76,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Safe! I was pretty cold back there, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.84,0:15:34.43,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry. Things are getting desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.51,0:15:36.68,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, desperate?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.76,0:15:40.39,Font 1,,0,0,0,,If we're unlucky, this whole\Nplace could burn down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.45,0:15:55.87,Font 1,,0,0,0,,When are you going back to Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.95,0:15:58.20,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Well, now, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.29,0:16:01.33,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Really? Let's go home together, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.41,0:16:03.75,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Wait, um, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.83,0:16:05.33,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.42,0:16:08.88,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I left my bag behind on my way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.96,0:16:13.09,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You mean back at the White House?\NWas anything important in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.18,0:16:16.26,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Presents, and clothes I like...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.35,0:16:20.02,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Then it's too bad, but you\Nshouldn't go back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.85,0:16:25.35,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Leave things to me. Will you\Nloan me enough for cab fare?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.02,0:16:30.32,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Okay, get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.40,0:16:31.78,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.86,0:16:34.53,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Take us to the police station, quick as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.57,0:16:37.53,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Why the police station?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.26,0:16:56.22,Font 1,,0,0,0,,So this passport's not fake, anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.14,0:17:05.27,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Here you go, ticket and passport.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.35,0:17:06.90,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You're well-traveled, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.98,0:17:08.90,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.98,0:17:11.90,Font 1,,0,0,0,,To think the embassy even booked us a flight...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.98,0:17:14.57,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I was secretly really nervous,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.65,0:17:17.95,Font 1,,0,0,0,,worrying about what'd happen\Nif they found out we lied...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.03,0:17:20.62,Font 1,,0,0,0,,We didn't lie about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.70,0:17:23.54,Font 1,,0,0,0,,And we properly reported the theft to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.62,0:17:26.92,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, the embassy\Nwouldn't have lent us plane fare.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.00,0:17:29.38,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Government officials are more\Ncold-hearted than you'd think.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.46,0:17:31.29,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.72,0:17:40.22,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Um, it feels like you've ended up\Nhelping me with a lot of things,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.30,0:17:43.60,Font 1,,0,0,0,,but can I ask you about one\Nthing that's been bugging me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.68,0:17:44.60,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.68,0:17:48.27,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What were you really doing\Nthere when I first met you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.35,0:17:50.90,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Staging some kind of protest?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.11,0:17:56.78,Font 1,,0,0,0,,The truth is, I'm a terrorist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.86,0:17:59.24,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Nah, just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.28,0:18:04.95,Font 1,,0,0,0,,See, that's a popular game among\Nthe exchange students over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.04,0:18:08.67,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Pretty awful how they make us carry\Nguns, huh? Even if they are fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.75,0:18:11.63,Font 1,,0,0,0,,That's a very extreme game.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.71,0:18:13.25,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.55,0:18:16.72,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What are you doing in D.C.?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.01,0:18:21.30,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Oh, I was on a college graduation trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.39,0:18:25.43,Font 1,,0,0,0,,It was a trip to New York, but I really\Nwanted to see the White House,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.52,0:18:28.39,Font 1,,0,0,0,,so I slipped away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.48,0:18:29.90,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.98,0:18:32.52,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Why the White House?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.61,0:18:38.61,Font 1,,0,0,0,,How should I put it...? I thought\Nmaybe it was the center of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.70,0:18:44.16,Font 1,,0,0,0,,That's strange, huh? I don't usually\Npay much attention to the U.S.,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.24,0:18:47.45,Font 1,,0,0,0,,but I started thinking maybe\Neverything from my little problems
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.54,0:18:53.00,Font 1,,0,0,0,,to the whole world situation was\Nconnected to this place at the root.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.63,0:18:58.72,Font 1,,0,0,0,,And there's something\Ngoing on in Japan, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.80,0:19:02.84,Font 1,,0,0,0,,A heavy atmosphere that we can't do\Nanything about ourselves anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.93,0:19:11.31,Font 1,,0,0,0,,So I thought I'd wish for them\Nto help us out, even a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.40,0:19:13.56,Font 1,,0,0,0,,And I interrupted you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.65,0:19:19.40,Font 1,,0,0,0,,No... I'd actually thought better\Nof it even before you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.49,0:19:24.70,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I realized this place has nothing to do with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.78,0:19:28.08,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I get you... not that I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.16,0:19:29.83,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What's that mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.21,0:19:35.29,Font 1,,0,0,0,,But a certain someone's little\Nterrorist act landed a blow for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.38,0:19:38.21,Font 1,,0,0,0,,and that's good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.97,0:19:44.43,Font 1,,0,0,0,,My johnny landed a blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.94,0:19:57.73,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I'm Saki Morimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.82,0:19:59.36,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.11,0:20:02.65,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.20,0:20:08.70,Font 1,,0,0,0,,"Akira Takizawa"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.66,0:20:11.58,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.66,0:20:16.38,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You were born on January 7th, 1 989--\Nyou're the same as me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.46,0:20:21.84,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Born during the last week of the\NShowa era, right before it became Heisei!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.92,0:20:26.22,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Huh, so you're in the Showa 64 gang too...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.30,0:20:31.06,Font 1,,0,0,0,,But since you were born on\Nthe seventh, I'm a day older.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.14,0:20:33.27,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Right, Takizawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.44,0:20:44.20,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Could Takizawa be my prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.33,0:20:49.62,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Nah, of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.62,0:20:55.75,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.83,0:21:01.09,Font 1,,0,0,0,,That "heavy atmosphere" you\Nwere talking about... is it this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.55,0:21:05.76,Font 1,,0,0,0,,A missile attack on Tokyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.60,0:21:15.39,Font 1,,0,0,0,,The night is a seal
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.48,0:21:22.86,Font 1,,0,0,0,,If we mix in some bewilderment, it will end
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.03,0:21:34.79,Font 1,,0,0,0,,If we're in danger of wavering,\Nlet's just abandon our reasons
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.08,0:21:42.50,Font 1,,0,0,0,,We drown in dreams again
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.88,0:21:46.59,Font 1,,0,0,0,,The future stretches on uncertainly
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.68,0:21:57.94,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I can still forgive you,\NI can still know the meaning
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.02,0:22:02.82,Font 1,,0,0,0,,The night exists to be listened to closely
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.90,0:22:08.95,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I can copy that reason, and change
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.03,0:22:19.75,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't mind cutting off\Nthe future to know your breath
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.83,0:22:25.01,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't mind cutting off the future